msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_FEDERATIONREMAINS_REAL\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"这闻起来就像个陷阱，你内心也有些犹豫，不愿去打扰这片或许已是数位战友安息之地"
