msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_LONELYDYNASTY_FIGHT_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr "这就让那些混蛋知道教训！无论在什么情况下，无礼之徒都该去死！至少你对此感到满"
"意，一边清点着战利品，一边准备离开信标。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:428
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_LONELYDYNASTY\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:434
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_LONELYDYNASTY_REAL\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"联邦成员很少会将灵朝舰船视作友善的存在……但这总归好过遇上另一艘满载无脑空壳怪"
"的飞船。显然，对方也是同样的想法，一名魂灵族发来通讯：“绝不可能！我从未想过，"
"看到活人的身影竟能让我振奋……可这里的无魂者，比我所见过的任何活人都要可怖。敢"
"问，是何缘由让你踏入这片星云炼狱？”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:437
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_LONELYDYNASTY_REAL\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "我倒也想问你同样的问题。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:439
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_LONELYDYNASTY_REAL\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"魂灵族嗤笑一声，“我还需要征得你的同意吗？如果你非要知道，我们是来此斩妖除魔的"
"……却不知潜藏其中的是更可怕的怪物。我们的人数已在它们卑劣的袭击中不断减少，一"
"想到又有人陨落、又有这些令人作呕的怪物诞生，我的心就为之颤抖。”气氛沉重了片刻"
"，魂灵族继续说道，“所以正因如此，我们才容忍你在这里，活人。资源紧缺，我们要尽"
"可能收集物资以便撤离，我们还有兄弟要悼念。”灵朝舰船向你开放了它们的货品，只要"
"你能忍受它们的出言不逊。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:441
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_LONELYDYNASTY_REAL\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_ALIGNED\"]/text"
msgstr "（灵魂瘟疫船员）被你叫作活人我可以忍，但侮辱我的船员就是另一回事了。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:443
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_LONELYDYNASTY_REAL\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_ALIGNED\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"一阵困惑过后，你的灵魂瘟疫阵营船员走进了房间，通讯另一端的魂灵族提高了音量，“"
"你竟然与怪物为伍？！我真是瞎了眼才会信任你这样的人……你的坟墓也会成为它们的归"
"宿！”灵朝舰船切断了通讯，武器系统随即启动！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:446
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_LONELYDYNASTY_REAL\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_ALIGNED\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:452
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_LONELYDYNASTY_REAL\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_GHOST\"]/text"
msgstr "（魂灵族船员）“求你，收回那些恶言！”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:454
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_LONELYDYNASTY_REAL\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_GHOST\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你的魂灵族船员从你身后喊道，通讯另一端的魂灵族稍稍后退，“怎会，我的耳朵在骗我"
"吗？一个活人竟会收留我们的族人，而且还是平等相待……这片炼狱依旧充满惊喜！资源"
"或许匮乏，没错，但在怪物的海洋里，还有什么比情谊更稀缺的？容许我们庆贺一番！”"
"两名魂灵族一见如故，他们给你发来一份纪念礼物，随后灵朝舰船便向你开放了货品。"
"不过，他们自始至终都没收回“活人”这个称呼……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:457
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_LONELYDYNASTY_REAL\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_GHOST\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:463
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_LONELYDYNASTY_REAL\"]/choice/event/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "闭上嘴，准备交易。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:465
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_LONELYDYNASTY_REAL\"]/choice/event/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr "你宁可忍气吞声，也不会恩将仇报……就算它们是魂灵族，周遭潜伏着的、还有远比它们"
"更恐怖、更名副其实的不死之物。你会能拿多少就拿多少。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:467
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_LONELYDYNASTY_REAL\"]/choice/event/choice[3]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:473
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_LONELYDYNASTY_REAL\"]/choice/event/choice[4]/text"
msgstr "不了，去他的。干掉这家伙。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:475
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_LONELYDYNASTY_REAL\"]/choice/event/choice[4]/event/text"
msgstr "如果他们真的一心只想活命，就不会到处侮辱善良勤恳的人。你切断通讯、启动武器，"
"准备付出更多“辛劳”，而那艘灵朝舰船也做出了同样的举动！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:478
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_LONELYDYNASTY_REAL\"]/choice/event/choice[4]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:490
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//ship[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_TIREDSLUG_FIGHT\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr "那艘船四分五裂，你迅速回收了你能找到的东西。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:493
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//ship[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_TIREDSLUG_FIGHT\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:498
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//ship[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_TIREDSLUG_FIGHT\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr "敌方船员尽数死亡，你迅速回收了你能找到的东西。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:501
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//ship[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_TIREDSLUG_FIGHT\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:508
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_TIREDSLUG_FIGHT_MERCY\"]/text"
msgstr "当蛞蝓族的舰船冒着浓烟，舰体距离崩解仅差分毫时，你收到了一通绝望的通讯：“等等"
"！也许你终究还是有自保之力的。也许该手下留情的不是我，而是你？”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:510
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_TIREDSLUG_FIGHT_MERCY\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "收手吧。你才是掌握仁慈的一方。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:512
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_TIREDSLUG_FIGHT_MERCY\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你放过了蛞蝓族，并解决了剩余的灵魂瘟疫空壳怪。一切平息之后，狼狈的蛞蝓族松了"
"口气：“你是～～第一个真正拦住那些怪物的人。第一个真正活下来的人！”他们笑着，"
"并未意识到自己已陷入疯狂，接着说道：“愿～～意的话就多待一会儿吧！我们在这里很"
"少有同伴……毕竟到处都是杀人的丧尸～～。”如果情况如此糟糕，你不禁好奇蛞蝓族和它"
"的船员为何还留在这里……无论答案如何，你都得到了一次交易的机会。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:518
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_TIREDSLUG_FIGHT_MERCY\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "战斗吧。你即是死神。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:524
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_TIREDSLUG_FIGHT_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr "蛞蝓族已死，你再也没有可以交易的对象了……不过你本来就不确定自己是否想和这群疯"
"子交易。他们显然已经在这片星云中丧失了理智，即便还没有丢掉性命。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:535
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_TIREDSLUG_WAITING_NORMAL\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"又过了一会儿，这次时间短得多，外面的撞击声突然停了……你看向那只蛞蝓族，它松了"
"口气说道：“我们～～应该能安全一阵子了。你是～～第一个真正听我话的人。第一个真"
"正活下来的人！”它笑着，并未意识到自己已经疯了，接着说道：“愿～～意的话就多待"
"一会儿吧！我们在这里很少有同伴……毕竟到处都是杀～～人的丧尸～～。”如果情况真的"
"这么糟糕，你不禁好奇这只蛞蝓族和它的船员为什么还留在这里……不管答案是什么，一"
"切都已平静下来，你得到了一次交易的机会。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:540
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_TIREDSLUG_WAITING_UNLUCKY\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"没完没了，没完没了，没完没了……这声音就没停过。你在死寂中度过了仿佛永恒的时间"
"，最终，外面的撞击声总算彻底平息了。你看向那只蛞蝓族，它松了口气说道：“我们～"
"～应该能安全一阵子了。你是～～第一个真正听我话的人。第一个真正活下来的人！”它"
"笑着，并未意识到自己已经疯了，接着说道：“愿～～意的话就多待一会儿吧！我们在这"
"里很少有同伴……毕竟到处都是杀～～人的丧尸～～。”如果情况真的这么糟糕，你不禁好"
"奇这只蛞蝓族和它的船员为什么还留在这里……不管答案是什么，一切都已平静下来，你"
"得到了一次交易的机会。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:553
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_TIREDSLUG\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:559
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_TIREDSLUG_REAL\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"一艘蛞蝓族舰船潜藏在附近的星云中，这景象通常会让任何舰船的船长心生恐惧……但你"
"此刻只在祈祷，这不是另一艘被空壳怪占据的船。当对方舰船发来通讯时，你松了口气"
"，但这份安心转瞬即逝，通讯那头的蛞蝓族朝你大喊：“滚出去！这里不～～安全！快～"
"～走！”你想，蛞蝓族向来就没什么好客之道……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:562
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_TIREDSLUG_REAL\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "试着让蛞蝓族冷静下来。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:564
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_TIREDSLUG_REAL\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你的努力毫无用处，它们依旧大喊着：“别～～说话！一个字都不～～许说！在我身边开"
"口的人都会遇～～到坏事……一直都是这样！而我阻～～止不了！”它们看起来有点……精神"
"错乱。你想，任谁在这里待久了都会变成这样。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:566
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_TIREDSLUG_REAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "向蛞蝓族保证你能照顾好自己。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:568
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_TIREDSLUG_REAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "蛞蝓族用脆弱的触手猛拍桌子，大喊道：“你没在听～～吗？闭～～嘴！！！”它的声音"
"里，疯狂之中又多了几分愤怒与急躁。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:570
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_TIREDSLUG_REAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "证明这只蛞蝓族是错的。发出点声音。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:572
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_TIREDSLUG_REAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你故作嘲讽地举起双手，轻轻喊了一声：“嘘——”！你的舰船内部立刻传来一阵剧烈的颠"
"簸，还有令人恐惧的金属摩擦声。蛞蝓族绝望地看着自己的触手：“为什么他们永远不～"
"～听？这是对我的惩罚吗？我是不是在地狱里……？”过了片刻，它把面条般的手臂攥成拳"
"头：“不！我～～还有选择……我绝不会让它们再把任何一个灵魂拉入它们扭曲的军团！我"
"即是救赎！我即是仁慈！大团的灵魂瘟疫感染黏液从天花板渗透下来，随即聚集成一小"
"支灵魂瘟疫空壳怪大军，而蛞蝓族的舰船也开始向你发起进攻！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:576
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_TIREDSLUG_REAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:582
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_TIREDSLUG_REAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "照做，保持安静。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:584
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_TIREDSLUG_REAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你听到金属发出嘎吱声，有什么东西在不断撞击你的舰船外壁。蛞蝓族稍微冷静了一些"
"，但语气依旧无比严肃：“它们已经来了……可你只要～～保持～～安静，它们或许就会离"
"开！”你暗自纳闷，这么大声喊真的有用吗。你和蛞蝓族就这样在寂静中等待着……时间一"
"点点过去，可舰船外的撞击声依旧没有停止。就这样坐在这里干等，真的值得吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:587
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_TIREDSLUG_REAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "坚持说你真的必须得走了。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:589
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_TIREDSLUG_REAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你一边想着叛军舰队正在逼近，一边尽力礼貌地告辞。你的舰船内部立刻传来一阵剧烈"
"震动，金属嘎吱声愈发刺耳。蛞蝓族绝望地看着自己的触手：“为什么他们永远不～～听"
"？这是对我的惩罚吗？我是不是在地狱里……？”过了片刻，它把面条般的手臂攥成拳头："
"“不！我～～还有选择……我绝不会让它们再把任何一个灵魂拉入它们扭曲的军团！我即是"
"救赎！我即是仁慈！”大团沾染灵魂瘟疫的黏液从天花板渗透而下，随即聚集成一小支灵"
"魂瘟疫空壳怪大军，而蛞蝓族的舰船也立刻向你发起进攻！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:593
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_TIREDSLUG_REAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:599
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_TIREDSLUG_REAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "继续安静等待。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:601
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_TIREDSLUG_REAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你和那只蛞蝓族就这样对视着，气氛有些尴尬，但你心里清楚，在这片该死的星云里，"
"比起糟糕透顶的遭遇，这点不愉快的社交尴尬甚至连沉默对峙都算不了什么。真正让你"
"不安的是那阵撞击声……一下，又一下，持续不断，没完没了。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:604
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_TIREDSLUG_REAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "对着那声音大喊。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:606
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_TIREDSLUG_REAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你一时没忍住，对着外面的撞击声破口大骂。你的舰船内部立刻传来一阵剧烈震动，金"
"属的嘎吱声变得更加刺耳。蛞蝓族绝望地看着自己的触手：“为什么他们永远不～～听？"
"这是对我的惩罚吗？我是不是在地狱里……？”过了片刻，它把面条般的手臂攥成拳头：“"
"不！我～～还有选择……我绝不会让它们再把任何一个灵魂拉入它们扭曲的军团！我即是"
"救赎！我即是仁慈！”大团被灵魂瘟疫感染的黏液从天花板渗透而下，随即聚集成一小支"
"灵魂瘟疫空壳怪大军，而蛞蝓族的舰船也立刻向你发起进攻！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:610
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_TIREDSLUG_REAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:616
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_TIREDSLUG_REAL\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "保持坚强。等待。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:628
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_TIREDSLUG_REAL\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "因为蛞蝓族的无礼，向它发起攻击。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:630
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_TIREDSLUG_REAL\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你才不会任由这个混蛋摆布。不管这里是不是被空壳怪占据的星云，你都有自己的底线"
"！你摆明了自己的态度，你的舰船内部立刻传来一阵剧烈颠簸，还有令人恐惧的金属摩"
"擦声。蛞蝓族绝望地看着自己的触手：“为什么他们永远不～～听？这是对我的惩罚吗？"
"我是不是在地狱里……？”过了片刻，它把面条般的手臂攥成拳头：“不！我～～还有选择…"
"…我绝不会让它们再把任何一个灵魂拉入它们扭曲的军团！我即是救赎！我即是仁慈！”"
"大团被灵魂瘟疫感染的黏液从天花板渗透而下，随即聚集成一小支灵魂瘟疫空壳怪大军"
"，而蛞蝓族的舰船也立刻向你发起进攻！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:634
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_TIREDSLUG_REAL\"]/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:640
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_TIREDSLUG_REAL\"]/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "听从蛞蝓族的话，赶紧离开。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:642
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_TIREDSLUG_REAL\"]/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr "你终止通讯，与那只疯狂的蛞蝓族拉开了极大距离。它的舰船渐渐消失在星云昏暗的深"
"处，而你不禁好奇，它到底遭遇了什么。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:644
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_TIREDSLUG_REAL\"]/choice[3]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "星舰管理。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:648
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_TIREDSLUG_REAL\"]/choice[3]/event/choice[2]/text"
