msgstr "那艘船四分五裂，你迅速回收了你能找到的东西。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:660
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//ship[@name=\"NEBULA_STORELIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_SLUGPARANOIA_REAL_FIGHT\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
