msgstr "你竭尽全力在外面的灵魂瘟疫黏液中机动操控，但一次失误就导致你的舰体撞上了一堆"
"受感染的物质……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1393
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_SWARMPRIZE_NAVIGATEGAMBLE_CRITICALLOSS\"]/choice/text"
