#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1935
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_ABANDONEDWEAPONS\"]/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_LANIUS\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你的食铁族小心地绕着武器进食，时刻留意着被灵魂瘟疫感染的物质，他们毫不费力就"
"将武器取了下来。然而，这一举动似乎依然触发了舰体残骸内被感染物质的反应……在你"
"取回武器时，灵魂瘟疫躯壳从华丽的黏液中升起，存心要给你制造麻烦！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1941
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_ABANDONEDWEAPONS\"]/choice[5]/text"
msgstr "尝试强行将残骸与武器分离开。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1945
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_ABANDONEDWEAPONS\"]/choice[6]/text"
msgstr "无视该武器。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1947
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_ABANDONEDWEAPONS\"]/choice[6]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"究竟是什么会让你迫切需要一把被灵魂瘟疫感染的武器？更别说你首先就得去扰动它所"
"附着的那块舰体残骸……你现在可没兴趣再跟更多的躯壳战斗。那块残骸继续在外面的星"
"云云雾中永恒漂流，你也得以获得一段休整的时间。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1949
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_ABANDONEDWEAPONS\"]/choice[6]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "星舰管理。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1953
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_ABANDONEDWEAPONS\"]/choice[6]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "跳过。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1961
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKTAMING_THINGSHAPPEN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你还没来得及做任何事，头顶的管道突然爆裂，一股浓稠黏腻的灵魂瘟疫感染黏液从天"
"花板倾泻而下；你堪堪侧身躲开，这道油腻的液体溅落在你身旁的地面上。液体流淌时"
"迅速变稀，直到其中的灵魂瘟疫感染物质逐渐消散，最后喷溅而出的只剩下水。希望这"
"至少意味着系统的其余部分没有被污染……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1964
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKTAMING_THINGSHAPPEN\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "震惊地盯着那滩积水。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1966
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKTAMING_THINGSHAPPEN\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"水流从头顶流过，你难以置信地盯着那滩泛着虹彩的积水。就在这时，你听到了什么声"
"音……一声低语。它问你，你的子嗣中你最偏爱哪一个，船员们的身影在你脑海中一一浮"
"现……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1968
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKTAMING_THINGSHAPPEN\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_CRYSTAL\"]/text"
msgstr "（水晶族船员）我的水晶子嗣……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1970
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKTAMING_THINGSHAPPEN\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_CRYSTAL\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你的视线变得模糊，随即陷入了昏迷。过了一段时间你醒来，看到一张熟悉的面孔……你"
"的水晶族船员，身影依旧有些模糊，正站在你身旁。你再也听不到水流声了……地板也没"
"有湿。刚才那一切难道都是你的幻觉吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1972
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKTAMING_THINGSHAPPEN\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_CRYSTAL\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "眨了几下眼睛。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1974
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKTAMING_THINGSHAPPEN\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_CRYSTAL\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你勉强镇定下来，眨了眨眼让视线清晰，随即发现那根本不是你的船员……而是一具灵魂"
"瘟疫躯壳！你受惊地向后爬去，在它抓住你之前重新站了起来……当然，前提是它真的打"
"算抓你。它就只是站在那里。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1976
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKTAMING_THINGSHAPPEN\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_CRYSTAL\"]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "先动手！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1978
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKTAMING_THINGSHAPPEN\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_CRYSTAL\"]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "你朝这具躯壳射击，它的身体扭曲变形躲开了攻击……看来你激怒了它！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1983
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKTAMING_THINGSHAPPEN\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_CRYSTAL\"]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "等着这具躯壳先行动。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:1985
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_ITEMS_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUSKTAMING_THINGSHAPPEN\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_CRYSTAL\"]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你迟疑着没有先动手，那具躯壳依旧只是站在那里。最后，它发出一阵奇怪的咕噜声，"
"随后走进了另一个房间……你的船员们都避开了它的路线，但它似乎对他们也毫无兴趣。"
"那么，这是一只友好的躯壳吗……？你那位新长着触手的同伴将一把餐叉整个吞进躯干里"
"，让你不禁好奇，是什么原因让这些怪物中的一部分变得温顺且易受影响。"

