#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2738
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_BUSYHUSKS_CENTEROFBUSINESS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"飞船群后方的星云空间，比你预想的要空旷得多。你不知道原因，但躯壳似乎在周围形"
"成了某种屏障……一颗巨大、油亮的球体，完全由被灵魂瘟疫感染的物质构成。当你进入"
"这片空旷区域并观察这颗奇异球体时，你的视线开始模糊……完全陌生的思绪涌入你的脑"
"海：\n"
"\n"
"“……加入我们……融为一体……”\n"
"“……你难道不进来……进入内部……”\n"
"“……获得自由……永远……在一起……”\n"
"\n"
"你不由自主地想要靠近那颗球体，任由它将你带走。让你与它合而为一……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2746
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_BUSYHUSKS_CENTEROFBUSINESS\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "是的，自由……永远……在一起……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2748
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_BUSYHUSKS_CENTEROFBUSINESS\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "你驾驶飞船向前驶去，那散发着微光的存在开始将你包裹。接纳你。你感到平静……温暖"
"，仿佛这里才是你的归宿。仿佛回到了家。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2751
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_BUSYHUSKS_CENTEROFBUSINESS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "我到家了……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2753
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_BUSYHUSKS_CENTEROFBUSINESS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"更多思绪涌向你，你的飞船向着这片奇妙的归宿沉得更深……\n"
"\n"
"“……属于我们……孩子……”\n"
"“……你到家了……孩子……”\n"
"“……永远自由……孩子……”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2760
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_BUSYHUSKS_CENTEROFBUSINESS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "永远……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2762
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_BUSYHUSKS_CENTEROFBUSINESS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“……永恒的极乐……与我们同在……”\n"
"“……永远幸福……在一起……”\n"
"“……不再有烦恼……在这乐园之中……”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2768
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_BUSYHUSKS_CENTEROFBUSINESS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2770
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_BUSYHUSKS_CENTEROFBUSINESS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"可就在这片全新的极乐之中，极其短暂的一瞬，你的思绪转向了别处。你想到了联邦，"
"想到了所有依靠着你的人。你想到了叛军 ，想到了他们所要对抗的一切。你甚至想到了"
"你自己，想到你所有曾渴望的一切，所有曾期盼的一切……而你意识到，就这样死去，绝"
"对不符合其中任何一件事的意义。你凝聚起体内每一分意志力，冲破脑海中的那些声音"
"，奋力伸手去触碰飞船的操控装置……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2772
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_BUSYHUSKS_CENTEROFBUSINESS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "把引擎开到最大功率！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2774
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_BUSYHUSKS_CENTEROFBUSINESS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"引擎轰鸣着启动，你的飞船挣脱了那颗被灵魂瘟疫感染的球体，传来一阵模糊不清、几"
"乎无法被你混乱的意识捕捉的声响。飞船猛地冲出球体，掠过躯壳群，随后向着星云深"
"处飞速驶离，持续了很长一段时间。最终，你勉强恢复清醒，将飞船停了下来……你刚才"
"究竟经历了什么？你是不是受到了某种心灵控制……？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2776
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_BUSYHUSKS_CENTEROFBUSINESS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "拍掉膝盖上的灰尘，松一口气。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2778
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_BUSYHUSKS_CENTEROFBUSINESS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"不管刚才发生了什么，至少你和飞船现在都安然无恙。有那么一瞬间，你在担心飞船被"
"大量灵魂瘟疫感染物质吞噬后可能产生的后果，但当你看到自己影子在扭动时，所有忧"
"虑都平息了下去。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2780
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_BUSYHUSKS_CENTEROFBUSINESS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "那……什么？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2782
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_BUSYHUSKS_CENTEROFBUSINESS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "的确，它在扭动，一如往常。正如你一直以来的模样。正如你一直渴望的模样。正如你"
"永远无法抵达的模样。你就是你，而你，早已归家。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2783
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_BUSYHUSKS_CENTEROFBUSINESS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/crewMember"
msgstr "你"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2785
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_BUSYHUSKS_CENTEROFBUSINESS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "没错。我到家了。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2787
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_BUSYHUSKS_CENTEROFBUSINESS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "你准备启动超光速引擎，看着自己离开这个房间。你今天在这里完成了一件了不起的事"
"，你理应感到自豪。你确实感到自豪。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2805
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_BUSYHUSKS_CENTEROFBUSINESS\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "抵抗那些声音，赶紧离开这里！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2807
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_BUSYHUSKS_CENTEROFBUSINESS\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你集中精神，将引擎开到最大功率，引擎轰然轰鸣，飞船冲破躯壳群，向着星云云层深"
"处疾驰而去。飞船飞行了许久，最终，你恢复镇定，将飞船停了下来……你刚才到底经历"
"了什么？你是不是受到了某种心灵控制……？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2809
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_BUSYHUSKS_CENTEROFBUSINESS\"]/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "拍掉膝盖上的灰尘，松一口气。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2811
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_BUSYHUSKS_CENTEROFBUSINESS\"]/choice[2]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "不管发生了什么，至少现在一切似乎都平静下来了。你别无选择，只能离开信标，继续"
"深入这片你身陷其中的地狱。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2819
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_BUSYHUSKS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"云层之中聚集着大批飞船，每一艘都在漫无目的地随意移动。或者说，至少是半随机地"
"移动。它们的注意力似乎都集中在被所有飞船环绕的某个物体上，但隔着这么多飞船，"
"根本无法看清那东西究竟是什么。无论如何，不难判断这些都是由灵魂瘟疫躯壳松散操"
"控的飞船，而且它们暂时还没有发现你的到来。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2822
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_BUSYHUSKS\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "也许有办法穿过它们……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2824
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_BUSYHUSKS\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "这些飞船像虫群一样围绕着的东西，让你很感兴趣。不过这里数量实在太多，你得制定"
"一个稳妥的计划才能突破过去。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2826
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_BUSYHUSKS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_ALIGNED\"]/text"
msgstr "(灵魂瘟疫船员) 也许我们可以靠交涉穿过这群飞船？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2830
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_BUSYHUSKS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"cloaking\"]/text"
msgstr "(高级隐形) 启动隐形，尝试悄悄穿过飞船群。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2834
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_BUSYHUSKS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"engines\"]/text"
msgstr "(高级引擎) 尝试冲破飞船群。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2838
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_BUSYHUSKS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[4]/text"
msgstr "好，我有计划了。冲过这群飞船！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2840
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_BUSYHUSKS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[4]/event/text"
msgstr "你丝毫不惧，展现出变元者最擅长的本事。你朝着躯壳飞船靠近时，其中几艘脱离编队"
"迎了上来，动作疯狂至极……要是不想被团团围住，你必须速战速决！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2844
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_BUSYHUSKS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[4]/event/triggeredEvent/triggeredEventBox/tooltip"
msgstr "在你成功突围之前，躯壳会不断涌入你的飞船！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2848
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_BUSYHUSKS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[4]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2854
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_BUSYHUSKS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[5]/text"
msgstr "算了……别去管这群飞船了。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2856
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_BUSYHUSKS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[5]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你终究还是觉得，所有穿过这群飞船的方案都不合心意。你决定暂且按兵不动，在等待"
"超光速引擎充能的同时，与躯壳飞船以及它们所围绕的未知事物保持安全距离。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2858
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_BUSYHUSKS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[5]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "星舰管理。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2862
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_BUSYHUSKS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[5]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "跳过。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2870
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_BUSYHUSKS\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "别去招惹那些躯壳。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2872
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_BUSYHUSKS\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "你没兴趣去对付数量这么庞大的躯壳飞船群。你打算静观其变，在等待超光速引擎充能"
"的过程中，与它们以及它们所围绕的东西保持距离。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2874
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_BUSYHUSKS\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "星舰管理。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2878
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_BUSYHUSKS\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "跳过。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2887
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//ship[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUNTINGGUILD_FIGHT\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr "那艘船四分五裂，你迅速回收了你能找到的东西。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2890
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//ship[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUNTINGGUILD_FIGHT\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2895
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//ship[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUNTINGGUILD_FIGHT\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr "敌方船员尽数死亡，你迅速回收了你能找到的东西。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2898
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//ship[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUNTINGGUILD_FIGHT\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2905
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUNTINGGUILD_FIGHT_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"既然异种猎人已经被击败，这个现实世界总算变得稍微安全一点了……不过，他们本来就"
"是来这里猎杀真正的怪物的，不是吗？你不确定这么做到底是助长了邪恶还是消灭了邪"
"恶，但……不管怎么说，他们本来就只是些混蛋。你很乐意收拾这些混蛋，就算他们本身"
"也在猎杀怪物。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2909
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUNTINGGUILD\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你在进入信标时，一道能量射向你，你堪堪避开……没过多久你就查明了来源：一艘属于"
"星盗异猎会的飞船，潜伏在附近的云层之中。躲过这场失败的伏击后，你惊讶地看到他"
"们发起通讯：“实在抱歉啊，联邦伙计。还以为你是那些异形怪物呢，对吧？”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2913
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUNTINGGUILD\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "啥？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2915
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUNTINGGUILD\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"那名异种猎人转动着眼柄，然后尽力把话说得更清晰一点：“我、我在跟你道歉呢，伙计"
"。刚才朝你开火，是以为你是那些长、长触手的爬行动物。”你猜他指的是灵魂瘟疫躯壳"
"，就算“长触手的爬行动物”用来形容蛞蝓族也同样贴切……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2917
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUNTINGGUILD\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "你是来这里猎杀躯壳的吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2919
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUNTINGGUILD\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "这一次，他们叹了口气才开口：“你们联邦佬都这么慢吞吞的吗？我都说得够明白了，不"
"是吗？说吧，你到底有什么事，还是就只是喜欢问个不停？”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2921
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUNTINGGUILD\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "你知道吗，我自己也算是个躯壳猎手……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2923
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUNTINGGUILD\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“是吗？那我猜你身上也藏着一两件战利品来证明自己？”躯壳的战利品……它们通常只会"
"留下一滩滩失活的、被灵魂瘟疫感染的物质。你能拿出什么来向这名异种猎人证明自己"
"？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2925
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUNTINGGUILD\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_ALIGNED\"]/text"
msgstr "（灵魂瘟疫船员）看好了，我活捉了一只被这种黏液感染的恶魔！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2927
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUNTINGGUILD\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_ALIGNED\"]/event/text"
msgstr "他们对你麾下这名与灵魂瘟疫为伍的船员现身感到震惊：“我自己都从没把握能活捉它们"
"，伙计。这活儿干得真漂亮，对吧？你是怎么做到的？”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2929
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUNTINGGUILD\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_ALIGNED\"]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "编一段英雄事迹。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2931
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUNTINGGUILD\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_ALIGNED\"]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你向这名异种猎人绘声绘色地讲述了你是如何“收服”这名船员的无比宏大又真实的故事"
"，他们全程听得目不转睛。故事讲完后，他们开口道：“伙计，这简直就是传奇！下次我"
"再碰到这些爬行者，非得试试你这‘吊扇手里剑’的招数不可！拿着，就为了这个我以后"
"能在公会里跟同伴吹嘘的故事，还有你给的窍门！”这名异种猎人送来了一些物资，你猜"
"想那是他们狩猎战利品的一部分。这个故事的寓意是：撒谎真爽！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2936
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUNTINGGUILD\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_ALIGNED\"]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "坚称这是商业机密。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2938
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUNTINGGUILD\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_ALIGNED\"]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你告诉这名异种猎人，你绝不可能把这种情报透露给竞争对手，他思索了片刻。随后他"
"精神一振：“那我就只好亲眼见识一下了，不是吗？这样我们就是伙伴了，伙伴可不是竞"
"争对手！”他直接传送了过来，当即摆出好几件战利品与武器，一副这里归他说了算的样"
"子，但你可不会对新船员的到来挑三拣四。伙伴就是伙伴！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2945
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUNTINGGUILD\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"GIFTLIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_WEAPONS\"]/text"
msgstr "（灵魂瘟疫武器）看好了，我缴获了这些该死玩意儿的武器！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2947
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUNTINGGUILD\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"GIFTLIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_WEAPONS\"]/event/text"
msgstr "他们看到你这把被灵魂瘟疫感染的武器，大为震惊：“伙计，这玩意儿真的安全吗？你真"
"是个疯子——不过这一点公会里的人都会佩服！你到底是怎么弄来的？”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2949
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUNTINGGUILD\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"GIFTLIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_WEAPONS\"]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "编一段英雄事迹。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:2951
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUNTINGGUILD\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"GIFTLIST_DDSOULPLAGUE_WEAPONS\"]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""

