msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"NEBULA_NEUTRAL_DDSOULPLAGUE_HUNTINGGUILD\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"dd_corruptor\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他们看到你这套被灵魂瘟疫感染的系统，大为震惊：“我听说过这东西！伙计，这玩意儿"
