#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml:4555
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddsoulplague.xml$//event[@name=\"CLEARING_DDSOULPLAGUE_EPSILONREMAINS\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"就算这里飘着的是用彩虹和糖果做的随机箱子，你也不会信任，更别说这是金属和锁链"
